'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #3970] on 3 May 2001 at 1:44:41 pm'!"Change Set:		FloatArrayFixesDate:			3 May 2001Author:			Andreas RaabMakes float arrays go through a new (and working) version of #primitiveHash"!!FloatArray methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ar 5/3/2001 13:02'!hash	| result |	<primitive:'primitiveHashArray' module: 'FloatArrayPlugin'>	result _ 0.	1 to: self size do:[:i| result _ result + (self basicAt: i) ].	^result bitAnd: 16r1FFFFFFF! !!MatrixTransform2x3 methodsFor: 'comparing' stamp: 'ar 5/3/2001 13:02'!hash	| result |	<primitive: 'primitiveHashArray' module: 'FloatArrayPlugin'>	result _ 0.	1 to: self size do:[:i| result _ result + (self basicAt: i) ].	^result bitAnd: 16r1FFFFFFF! !